## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-731"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>类在 .NET Framework 2.0 中已过时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-731">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in .NET Framework 2.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-732">您可以 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 使用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> 类和方法创建验证实例 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-732">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-733">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 引用页的“备注”部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-733">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-734">用户需要测试返回的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-734">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-735">例如，</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-735">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-736">如果正在执行 XML 架构验证， `XmlSchemaType` 或对应于 `XmlSchemaDatatype` 正在读取的当前元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-736">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-737">如果 (DTD 验证) 正在执行文档类型定义，则此属性返回 `null` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-737">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-738">`XmlSchemaDatatype` 如果当前元素或特性是一个简单类型，它可以指定对简单类型的特殊验证约束（如 min 和 max），则返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-738">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-739">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` 如果当前元素或属性是用户定义的 simpleType，则返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-739">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-740">`XmlSchemaComplexType` 如果当前元素是用户定义的 complexType，则返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-740">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-741">特性无法返回此类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-741">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-742">如果已 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> 设置为 ValidationType，则不会从架构或 dtd 提供任何数据类型信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-742">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7a4b8-743">调用后 <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A> ，SchemaType 将返回 Null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7a4b8-743">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
